window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Cole Ellis hits a coyote late one night on I-80, he has no idea how his life will change.</p> <p>Now he travels to a dream realm every time he falls asleep…but all is not well in the drowsing world.</p> <p>There’s mystical talking animals, mysteriously bruised houses, and massive hulking monsters to deal with. How can a stay-at-home dad hope to save the neighborhood by naptime’s end?</p> <p>Or is it all in his head?</p> <p>Join the Stay-at-Home Shaman in the first story of an exciting new miniseries set in the Dark Prairie Universe.</p>"; 
